{"tid":2507310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國務院放寬禁令，中國留學生八月起可赴美","createTime":"2021-04-28T02:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T03:57:22.000Z","uid":278587,"like":3,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"a4c068bd7a6edbb9561853816c850390df932bd1","tid":2507310,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:24:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=432744\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432744&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0qC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=f2b89c7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D432744&h=e9f1e7a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=432744</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國最快八月讓中國留學生到當地上課。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發布通知，指由八月開始，持有有效F-1或M-1簽證的人員，可以乘坐直航航班入境美國，而毋須事先聯繫使館申請「國家利益豁免條件」。<br />\n<br />\n因應新冠疫情，美國目前禁止兩星期內到過中國、巴西、南非、伊朗及部分歐洲國家的大部分非美國公民入境，上月率才放寬對歐洲學生的相關限制，如今進一步為上述包括中國等地的學生放行，他們可以在今年秋季學期開始前30天內到美國。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國現行規定，所有入境者必須持最近72小時新冠病毒陰性檢測證明。"},{"pid":"ec3a76df2841402a3778487aec4b88016e7bc692","tid":2507310,"uid":370061,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:26:29.000Z","msg":"拜登對中強硬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596242baca6ce57e58ab5512b00a8db697a41eea","tid":2507310,"uid":76455,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec3a76df2841402a3778487aec4b88016e7bc692","tid":2507310,"uid":370061,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:26:29.000Z","msg":"拜登對中強硬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:32:28.000Z","msg":"要先要有簽證！"},{"pid":"b136a301a5993a3aec36d160fa34b9c7a01243e6","tid":2507310,"uid":121146,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T02:37:22.000Z","msg":"講左N次  